I'm currently using Font Awesome 4.7.0.  I hope the maintaining team can consider the following change:

## **Proposed changing**
Current:
```css
.fa {
  (...)
  text-rendering: auto;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
}
```

Modified:
```css
.fa {
  (...)
}

.fa::before {
  text-rendering: auto;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
}
